Review:
It was childish....if i was 10 or 15 i would love the energy and all the action
but as a 22 years old marvel fan i should mention that the actors did a good job but movie itself was very crowded and overwhelming, and popular cinematic elements were used extensively. Tobey and the other old characters were really funny but as i said childish. The love affair between Tom and his girlfriend was very cliché, and honestly all the romantic scenes in the movie I had to try not to close my eyes. But it is worthy of watching {just one time}
sorry if there is any mistake...English is my second language.
